dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents the aldermanic districts for Milwaukee, Wisconsin in 2018. The dataset was originally published by Milwaukee County Land Information Office (MCLIO) in 2016. The dataset was last updated on April 30, 2018. [This layer contains the boundaries of Municipal Aldermanic Districts in Milwaukee County.]
